&lt;li&gt;Serve as the California Airport market sub lead, collaborating with the Market Leader (ML), Practice Leaders (PLs) and Business Group Directors (BGDs) to develop a regional growth strategy to elevate client service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead business development efforts to secure new projects, expand the client base, and build long-term partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate and maintain strong client relationships with airport operators, public agencies, teaming partners, and private developers.&lt;/li&gt;
